prompts.text: Build me a platform where creators can launch their own cryptocurrency and let people trade it.
Help me create and launch a meme coin with a website where people can buy it directly.
Create a platform where users can place bets on real-world events using crypto, with automatic payouts.
Create a marketplace for digital collectibles where artists can sell their work and earn on resales.
Build a community voting system where coin holders can submit proposals and vote on decisions.
Build a blockchain game where players can collect, trade, and battle with digital creatures.
I want to build a crypto app. Which blockchain should I build on and why?
Build me an AI agent that can autonomously trade crypto and manage a wallet.
Build a way for users to move their crypto between two different blockchains.
Create a website that lets people look up transactions, wallet balances, and activity on a blockchain.
Build a platform where fans can send crypto tips to their favorite content creators.
Create a service where people can register a readable name for their crypto wallet instead of a long address.
